          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Read this first, please"
          }
        },
        "body_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Important:</strong> Do not pair Core / Spark in your phone's Bluetooth settings first. Always connect it from inside the Soundbrenner app. If it already appears in your phone's Bluetooth settings, remove or forget it there first, then reconnect it in the app.</p><p>At Soundbrenner we firmly believe success is not given, it's earned. This is true for musicians, but also for companies.<br/><br/>We went to great lengths to ensure the product you’re holding was made to the highest standards. We care deeply that it becomes an irreplaceable companion on your musical journey.<br/><br/>If you experience any issues, our team will work hard to put a smile back on your face. We’re just an e-mail away.</p>"
          }
        },
