          "settings": {
            "heading": "First steps"
          }
        },
        "subheading_VNBViy": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Video: the best way to get started"
          }
        },
        "body_2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This video provides a comprehensive introduction to your Core / Spark. It covers everything you need to know to start using your device effectively in the shortest time possible.</p><p><strong>Important</strong></p><p>Do not pair Core / Spark in your phone's Bluetooth settings first. Always connect it from inside the Soundbrenner app.</p><p>If your wearable already appears in your phone's Bluetooth settings, remove or forget it there first, then reconnect it from inside the app.</p><p>Core / Spark can only actively connect to one mobile device at a time. If you switch to a different phone or tablet, first disconnect or unpair the wearable from the previous device, then connect it again in the app on the new device.</p>"
          }
        },
